,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":187,"content":"| `attach_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → Profile.Board 增加 pending；目标 voicemail → push VoicemailGenStack（**不写 Board**） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":189,"content":"| `schedule_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → 写入 once intent，到点 `agent_outbound`；目标 voicemail → once intent，到点入栈/物化进信箱（**非**外呼） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":191,"content":"| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | **废弃**：校验拒绝；运行时不执行新写。旧 stub 读路径可过渡，不得作为新写真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":206,"content":"### 8.4 attach / schedule 对 voicemail 的分流","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":212,"content":"| 非 `voicemail` | 写 `Board.pending` | `agent_outbound` 响铃语义（现状） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":213,"content":"| `voicemail` | push **VoicemailGenStack**；**禁止**写 Board | 入栈/物化进信箱；**禁止** `agent_outbound` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":217,"content":"- 把 voicemail Instance 写入 `callCards.board.byAgent.*.pending`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":227,"content":"1. 出栈；加载卡定义；确认 `cardKind=voicemail`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":230,"content":"4. 写 `Profile.telephony.voicemails[]`（text 与/或 audioRef）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":264,"content":"- 目标 **非** voicemail：越过后生成 `agent_outbound`（外呼响铃）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":265,"content":"- 目标 **是** voicemail：越过后入 GenStack / 物化进信箱（**不是**外呼）；见 §8.4。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":17,"totalMatchedLines":17,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-1e40d524-fb4e-4c56-ae1c-75dc36f6452e-23\nfc_54a7d107-6ad1-97a7-96ef-3630b56a9c33_4","startedAtMs":"1784788060847","completedAtMs":"1784788061274"},"model_call_id":"9297e13c-49